snippet.title: What RUINED Family Guy?
snippet.description:
Family Guy has gone down in quality over the years and has lost millions of viewers. What exactly is the reason for this and why does Fox refuse to let the show end?

"What RUINED/What's RUINING..." is a video series where Saber researches a topic, presents its history, and how it is or was presumably ruined: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLrtmY8lRImW_58wGRjcJFUDFwFmHhtu1n
